# UI/UX Designer Position

We're looking for a creative and detail-oriented UI/UX Designer to join our team and help create exceptional user experiences for our games.

## What You'll Do

- Design intuitive and visually appealing user interfaces for games
- Create wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity mockups
- Conduct user research and usability testing
- Collaborate with developers to implement designs
- Maintain and evolve our design system
- Present design concepts to stakeholders

## Ideal Candidate

- Passionate about gaming and user experience
- Strong visual design skills with attention to detail
- Experience with responsive and adaptive design
- Understanding of accessibility principles
- Excellent communication and collaboration skills

## Benefits

- Flexible part-time schedule
- Opportunity to work on diverse gaming projects
- Collaborative and supportive team environment
- Professional growth opportunities
